<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA523_07_SU_0003_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema523_su_07.css" />
  <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema523_07_0003.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_07_su_0003">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="1_pink">
        <div>
          <span lang="y">글자 작품에는 어떤 특징이 있는지 알아봅시다.</span>
          <button type="button" class="icon_supplies" lang="y" data-supplies="pop_supplies_area_1">준비물</button>
        </div>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <div class="pop_area pop_supplies_area pop_supplies_area_1">
      <div class="supplies_zoom_wrap">
        <button type="button" class="close"></button>
        <div class="supplies_zoom scrollable">
          <div class="supplies_box_wrap">
            <div class="supplies_box">
              <div class="supplies_tit">글자</div>
              <div class="supplies_contents">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0003_supplies.png" alt="준비물 도형 - ㄹ" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="controller">
            <button class="supplies_scale_down" disabled></button>
            <button class="supplies_scale_up"></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="flex align_start gap_26">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">글자를 오른쪽의 글자에 완전히 겹치도록 포갠 후 표시된 점을 중심으로 180˚ 돌려 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="cont_box">
            <div class="dragndrop_fraction_wrap figure_wrap">
              <div class="drag_group figure_group1">
                  <div class="drag_item figure_triangle dragpable" data-pair="1" data-value="180">
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0003_content01.png" alt="ㄹ 이미지" class="img">
                    <button class="btn_rotation"><span>회전버튼</span></button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="drop_group figure_group2">
                  <div class="drop_item figure_triangle droppable" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="180"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text_box">
              <span class="img"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0003_content03.png" alt="이미지"></span>
              <span class="text" lang="y">180°<br>돌려 보자.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      <article class="page page_2">
        <h3 lang="y">처음 글자와 완전히 겹치는지 확인해 보세요.</h3>
        <div class="question_box mt_20 justify_center">
          <span lang="y">처음 글자와 완전히</span>
          
          <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown"  data-answer-single="겹칩니다.">
                  <option value=""> </option>
                  <option value="겹칩니다.">겹칩니다.</option>
                  <option value="겹치지 않습니다.">겹치지 않습니다.</option>
              </select>
          </div>
      </div>
      </article>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
    </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>